Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:38.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,よく分からない機械はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こういう所は結構綺麗だね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.69,0:00:43.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと閉じてたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:50.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんな場所なら　何か昔のことでも分かったりするのかなと思ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:53.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔のことって　例えば？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:58.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の人々がどんな暮らしをしていたのか…とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,服とか言葉とかさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなこと知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:16.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういえば　ヌコがいないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　たまにどっか行くよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また爆弾か何か食べてるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,気になる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:30.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,たまにさ　誰かと会って三人になったりするじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,イシイとかカナザワに会ったり？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコもそうだけど　少し違う雰囲気になるなーと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:39.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,賑やかというか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.20,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人だけだと寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんは寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:50.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まあ　少しは　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:53.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この入れ物の感じはまさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いてててて…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれの匂いがする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かな　なんか黒いけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べられるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べられる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:27.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:33.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,う…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.27,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これってあの味だよね　チョコの味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,甘い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.28,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食べ物のことはよく覚えているんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:52.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,もしかして　これがチョコなのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　チョコ味の何かでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　ある意味それも昔のことなのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,味も情報だなと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　記録できないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい　チー…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかカメラに文字が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,接続できる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　ヌコ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん　これ私たちが撮った写真だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カメラの中身を映しているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:54.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,空中に？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな機能が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　見て　懐かしい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,懐かしいっていうほど前じゃないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.81,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは何だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この写真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:17.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちが撮ったやつじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　これ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お　地図の人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,カナザワな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,と…隣りにいる女の人は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この辺の写真　カナザワが撮ったのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちと会った時は一人だったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,フォルダ　たくさんある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,フォルダ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部見よう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.93,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,全部開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっ　ちょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごい　人がいっぱいいる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:11.48,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これ…全部カメラの中に入ってたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:12.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えーそれでは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,動いた　喋った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ど…動画っていうやつかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,機械進化論研究会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,第十二回報告を始めます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,撮れてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.08,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,オッケーオッケー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:41.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,えー　今回のサンプルはこの小型機械です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちはこの機械　十七番乙種と名付けました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:52.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この種は生産設備に対し　あるプログラムを注入することにより
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,強制的に自らを増殖します
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちと同じくらいの歳の女の子だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.72,TEXT-JP-UP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,このような複雑な
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.91,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,プロセスが変異と淘汰で生まれることは考えづらく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.99,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこは進化でいいよねってことになったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の設計にしては利己的すぎるって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ？そうだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこ大事なとこじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:19.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:26.87,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでちーちゃんが昔のこと知りたがるのか　少し分かったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの…私お腹すいた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たち　ずっと二人っきりだけどさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:48.97,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こうして人々が暮らしてたんだなってことが分かると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほーらミドリ　パパだぞー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,パパのこと嫌いって言ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだその口の利き方は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.25,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.21,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめなさいって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,パンチ　おいでー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.89,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,本日　隣国に宣戦布告し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:39.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　もう一度意見調整してから報告するということで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,言ってないだろ　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大規模な空襲が…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　パパのせいだよー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:09.03,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我が軍は大勝利を収め　隣国の死者は五億人を超える
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,というわけで　ポテトを買ってきましたー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたってさー　意外と食い意地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.67,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,電磁波爆弾の使用を通告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,すべての電子機器はその機能が失われ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.57,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一着はミキちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,Happy bir…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,各都市　各階層との通信が途絶し
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,主よ　あなたの下に召された兄弟と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,永久の喜びを分かち合えますように
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,少しだけ寂しくない気がするね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,配管置き場を抜けられるのはお前たちぐらいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,上に登りなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人なら少ない食料で長く生きられる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.76,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじいさんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.41,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く行きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ヌコはまたいないな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれはどういう生き物なんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.31,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,扉を開けたり　機械を操作したり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,受信機を通して会話するし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　どうでもいいかー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,いたいた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　どこに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.79,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんかデカくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,デカイ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.78,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　ヌコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.00,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしよう…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お…追いかけなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.33,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前も私を食べるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.55,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの受信機がないと喋れないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.52,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はあのデカイやつと会話できないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつにユーを吐き出してくれって頼めないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私の言ってること分かる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はまだ小さいだけで　本当は人間の敵なのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:15.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.54,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,敵ってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:35.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.43,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.17,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,今行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.37,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユーがいなくなったら　私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.09,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.70,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ユー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.13,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？食べられたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.15,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんか頑張ったら出れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.58,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,頑張ったって…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は生きている人間を食べたりはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こいつが喋っているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は発声器官を持たないが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.16,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,音波を言語として解読することができる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.60,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから　この船の設備を利用している
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:33.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,幼体は通信範囲が狭いせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,稀にそういうことが起きる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:55.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これは我々の通信シグナルの一部を機械が受信したものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:58.42,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前たちは一体何なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしてユーを呑み込んだの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:06.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々が呑んだのはその人間が持っていた小型機械だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.65,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ホントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:14.44,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,古代の機械には　小型でも高エネルギーを持っているものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は熱的に不安定な物質を取り込み
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:31.02,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,体内で分解して　より静的な状態に安定させる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この処理が終わった時　地球は生命の長い営みを終えて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.80,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,再び眠りにつくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,その時　我々も眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.74,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この都市での活動はほとんど終えた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,都市の武器を全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて都市はゆっくりと停止してゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,停止って？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:16.22,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,我々は最上層以外ほとんどの場所を観測しているが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:20.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,現在生きている人間は君たち二人しか知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.53,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,その子を届けてくれて　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私たちは群れで行動する必要がある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.88,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんでヌコがびびってるのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.19,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前はいいな　仲間がたくさんいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さよなら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.10,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.59,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,地球終わるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:15.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,世界が終わろうと　どうでもいいことだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私とユーがいれば　それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.18,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.90,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.49,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,この歌声　あいつらのものだったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.38,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと絶望と仲良くなったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.95,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから悲しげなんだ　終わりの歌だから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.40,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.62,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,せーの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:26.30,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,食堂に缶詰があって良かったね　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.26,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.07,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,また二人だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.92,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,これまでも　これからも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.86,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人だけど寂しい？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.72,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんが寂しいんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:46.12,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私はユーが寂しいかと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.45,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,またまたー　素直じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.63,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は寂しくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.61,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちーちゃんがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,私もだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.32,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.56,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,行くぞ　早く乗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.06,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,あーい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.84,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,で　どこへ行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.46,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一番上に決まってるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.24,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね　上に何があろうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.01,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何もないかもしれないけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.14,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこに階層があるから登るのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.35,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.82,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,さて　どっちから行くかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.71,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:47.64,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっち
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:52.04,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,風の吹くまま　それも悪くないな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.50,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだ　ちーちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.34,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,一番上に行ったらさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.66,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしたらその次は月に行こうよ　月に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.98,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,月？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:11.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,行こうって言ったのちーちゃんじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.47,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.13,0:22:15.77,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　月か　それもいいか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.05,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,約束だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:17.69,TEXT-JP G-OTF Shin maru Go Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.51,0:00:38.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,先不說那些莫名其妙的機器
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這種地方倒還挺整潔的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.69,0:00:43.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因為一直是封閉的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.73,0:00:50.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我還以為只要來這種地方 就能知道些以前的事呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.06,0:00:53.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前的事？比如說？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.14,0:00:58.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,比如以前的人是怎麼生活的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再比如他們穿什麼 說什麼語言
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳會想知道這些呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.74,0:01:16.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,話說 錨不見了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.11,0:01:19.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊 牠偶爾會到處亂跑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是不是又在吃炸彈了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳很在意嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.25,0:01:30.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們有時不是會遇上別人 然後變成三人行嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳是指見到石井和金澤那會？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,錨在的時候也一樣 多一個人氣氛就會變好不少
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.17,0:01:39.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,會變得更熱鬧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.20,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只有兩個人的時候妳很寂寞？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳呢 妳會覺得寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.57,0:01:50.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 有點吧 但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.95,0:01:53.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,看這包裝 感覺裡面應該是…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.46,0:02:03.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有那東西的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那東西？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.67,0:02:08.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,真的能吃嗎 看起來好黑
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.26,0:02:14.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能吃的東西
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就是能吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.14,0:02:27.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.19,0:02:33.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.70,0:02:35.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.27,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這就是那個 巧克力的味道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.28,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有關食物的事妳倒是記得很清楚啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.52,0:02:52.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒準 這就是巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不 應該只是巧克力味的某種食物吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.03,0:03:04.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不過 這應該也算是過去的事情吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳指什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我想 味道也是訊息的一種
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,雖然沒法記錄下來
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好 茄…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,螢幕上出現了文字
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,可以連接
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 錨
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.67,0:03:48.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千 這些是我們之前拍的照片
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.58,0:03:52.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是把照相機裡的內容全顯示出來了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.51,0:03:54.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,而且是在空中？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,竟然還有這種功能
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 快看 好懷念啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這才過了多久啊 有什麼好懷念的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.81,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這些照片
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.97,0:04:17.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是我們拍的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 看這個
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是畫地圖的人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,人家叫金澤
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.22,0:04:28.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,他…他旁邊的女孩是誰啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.78,0:04:29.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這些照片 都是金澤拍的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,和我們認識的時候 他明明是一個人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有很多 文件夾
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.90,0:04:42.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,文件夾？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,全看一遍吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.93,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,全部都能打開
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好厲害 居然有這麼多人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.42,0:05:11.48,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這些全部都是照相機裡的內容嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.09,0:05:12.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,動起來了 說話了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這…這就是所謂的視頻嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,機器進化論研究會
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,第十二次報告 現在開始
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在拍嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.08,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.51,0:05:41.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯 這次的樣本是這個小型機器
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們將它命名為17號乙種機器
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.72,0:05:52.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這種機器能夠通過往生產設備中添加某種程序
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,強行實現自我繁殖
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是和我們差不多歲數的女孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.72,TEXT-CN-UP 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,很難想像
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.91,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,如此複雜的過程是通過變異和淘汰產生的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.89,0:06:05.99,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是說好要把這理解為機器的進化嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,畢竟 人為的設計應該不會這麼利己
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這點是很重要的好嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.26,0:06:19.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.78,0:06:26.87,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我好像有點明白 妳為什麼想知道以前的事情了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那個 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,現在？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.83,0:06:34.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們一直都是兩個人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.03,0:06:48.97,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但一旦知道以前的人都是這樣生活的…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快看 小綠 我是爸爸哦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,她在說她討厭爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,給我放尊重點
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.25,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳這個混蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.21,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,給我放手
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,波奇 過來
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.89,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,今日 我國向鄰國宣戰
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.13,0:07:39.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們就等綜合好意見之後再報告吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.81,0:07:52.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我根本沒這麼說過
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,大規模空襲…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你看 都怪爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.14,0:08:09.03,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我軍取得大勝 鄰國共損失5億人口
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,於是 我買了薯條回來
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒想到妳這麼貪吃
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.67,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,通知 即將使用電磁波炸彈
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所有的電子設備都將無法使用
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.57,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,第一名是美希
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.00,0:08:42.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,祝妳生日快樂
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,祝妳生…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,與各城市 各樓層的通訊全數中斷
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,主啊 請允許那些前往天國的兄弟們
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,與您共享永恆的快樂
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.18,0:09:12.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就會稍稍覺得不那麼寂寞了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.82,0:09:35.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能穿過廢管堆放場的就只有妳們了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,到上層去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,妳們的話 靠著不多的糧食也能活很久
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.76,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,爺爺你呢
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.41,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.41,0:10:10.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,錨又不見了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.85,0:10:14.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,牠到底是什麼生物呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.31,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能開門 能操縱機器
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,還能通過接收器說話
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,算了 管它呢
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我說 你到底跑…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.79,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有點大啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.78,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,咦 錨？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.86,0:10:51.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.00,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.69,0:11:17.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,得…得追上去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.33,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你也會吃掉我嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.55,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒有接收器你就沒法講話嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.52,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你能想辦法和那個大傢伙溝通嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.29,0:12:00.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能拜託牠把小尤吐出來嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,能聽懂我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你只是還小 長大後說不定也是人類的敵人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.21,0:12:15.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,敵人…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.54,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,什麼是敵人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.06,0:12:35.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.43,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.17,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我這就過去
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.37,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤不在的話 我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.26,0:13:40.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.09,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.72,0:14:38.70,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小千
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,小尤
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.13,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 妳都被吃掉了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.15,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,稍微努力一下就出來了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.58,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,努力一下…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們不會吃掉活生生的人類
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這個聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是這傢伙在講話嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.94,0:15:17.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們沒有發聲器官
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.16,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,但是可以將聲波解讀為語言
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.60,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以 我們借用了這艘船的設備
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.02,0:15:33.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幼體的通訊範圍十分有限
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以偶爾會發生這種事
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這首歌…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.90,0:15:55.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這是機器在接收到我們的部分訊號後發出的聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.15,0:15:58.42,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你們到底是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.94,0:16:00.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,為什麼要把小尤吞下去
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.32,0:16:06.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們吞掉的是那個人類身上的小型機器
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.65,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,啊 真的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.11,0:16:14.44,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,有些古代機器雖小 但也蘊含著大量能量
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們吸收熱不穩定物質
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.04,0:16:31.02,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,在體內分解 使其成為更穩定的物質
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,處理完畢後 地球的漫長生命將迎來終結
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.80,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再次進入休眠
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.73,0:16:59.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那時我們也會沉睡
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.74,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們已基本完成應在這座城市中開展的工作
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,城市裡的武器全被吞了？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這座城市也將逐漸停止運轉
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,停止？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.22,0:17:16.22,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們一直在觀察頂層以外的所有樓層
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.28,0:17:20.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,據我們所知 目前還活著的就只有妳們兩個
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.53,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們把牠送過來
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我們需要群體行動
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.88,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,為什麼錨會害怕啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.10,0:18:09.19,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,你真幸福啊 有這麼多夥伴
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.10,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我說 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.82,0:18:47.59,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,牠說地球會進入休眠
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.32,0:19:15.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,就算世界末日來了 對我們來說也無所謂
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只要我們還在一起 就夠了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.18,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.90,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.49,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,原來是牠們在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.38,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,絕望估計已經是牠們的老朋友了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.95,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,所以聽著才會覺得那麼悲傷 畢竟是首末日之歌
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.30,0:19:47.40,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.62,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.50,0:20:26.30,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,幸好食堂裡還有些罐頭啊 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.26,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.07,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又只剩我們兩個了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.92,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,以前是這樣 以後也不會變
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.86,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這樣妳很寂寞？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.69,0:20:41.72,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,寂寞的是妳吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.06,0:20:46.12,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我是怕妳會寂寞
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.45,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,又來了 一點都不坦率
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.63,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我一點都不寂寞哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.61,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,因為有妳在
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.96,0:21:05.32,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.56,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,要走了 快上車
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.06,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.84,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們要去哪？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.46,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,當然是去頂層
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.24,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,也是啊 先不管上面會有些什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.01,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,說不定什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.14,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,只要還沒到頂 我們就得繼續爬
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.35,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.93,0:21:32.82,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,好了 該往哪邊走呢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.71,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.06,0:21:47.64,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.34,0:21:52.04,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,迎風向前 這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.50,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,對了 小千
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.86,0:22:03.34,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,等我們爬到了頂層
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.64,0:22:06.66,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,接下來就去月亮吧 去月亮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.98,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,月亮？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.23,0:22:11.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不是妳自己說要去的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.47,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,我說過嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.13,0:22:15.77,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,不過 去月亮似乎也不錯
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.05,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,那說好了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.18,0:22:17.69,TEXT-CN 浪漫雅圆,,0,0,0,,嗯
